<item>
            <title>[FELIX-2188] Layout problems with old pluggins</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-2188</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;With the recent changes to the web console, old plugins might look very ugly and unexpected. I guess this is due to missing css classes&lt;br/&gt;
The best example is the event plugin &lt;/p&gt;</description>
